1、./configure 后会碰到not found glog的问题，解决步骤
   a、注释掉configure.ac 中的AC_MSG_ERROR相关的invalid检查的代码
   b、./configure CPPFLAGS="-I/usr/local/include" LDFLAGS="-L/usr/local/lib"
2、./configure通过后，make过程出现新的问题：
   libtool: compile:  g++ -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -I./.. -pthread -I/usr/include -I/usr/local/include -std=gnu++0x -g -O2 -MT FileUtil.lo -MD -MP -MF .deps/FileUtil.Tpo -c FileUtil.cpp  -DDLL_EXPORT -DPIC -o .libs/FileUtil.o
   libtool: compile:  g++ -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -I./.. -pthread -I/usr/include -I/usr/local/include -std=gnu++0x -g -O2 -MT FileUtil.lo -MD -MP -MF .deps/FileUtil.Tpo -c FileUtil.cpp -o FileUtil.o >/dev/null 2>&1
   make[2]: *** No rule to make target 'generate_fingerprint_tables', needed by 'FingerprintTables.cpp'。 停止。
   make[2]: Leaving directory '/home/wdthome/folly/folly'
   Makefile:1354: recipe for target 'all-recursive' failed
   make[1]: *** [all-recursive] Error 1
   make[1]: Leaving directory '/home/wdthome/folly/folly'
   Makefile:863: recipe for target 'all' failed
   make: *** [all] Error 2
   
   猜测是Makefile中有关generate_fingerprint_tables生成所依赖的文件路径设置问题，但查看MakeFile并没有发现错误。
   
   准备在mac上单独编译一遍folly，观察是否有问题。
   
   mac上编译通过了，主要碰到两个问题，
   1）与cygwin上碰到的问题一样，./configure 需要加选项，主要修改的文件为./build/bootstrap-osx-homebrew.sh，修改如下所示：
      
    !/bin/bash -x
     # The only prerequisite should be homebrew. If something doesn't work out of
     # the box with just homebrew, let's fix it.
   
      # fail fast
     set -e
    
     BASE_DIR="$(cd "$(dirname -- "$0")"/.. ; pwd)"  # folly/folly
     cd "$BASE_DIR"
  
     brewget() {
         brew install $@ || brew upgrade $@
      }
    
    # tool dependencies: autotools and scons (for double-conversion)
    brewget autoconf automake libtool
    
    # dependencies
    brewget glog gflags boost libevent double-conversion
    
    autoreconf -i
    ./configure CPPFLAGS="-I/usr/local/include" LDFLAGS="-L/usr/local/lib" LIBS="-lcrypto -ldl"
    
    #pushd test
    #test -e gtest-1.7.0.zip || {
    #    curl -O https://googletest.googlecode.com/files/gtest-1.7.0.zip
    #    unzip gtest-1.7.0.zip
    #}
    #popd
 
 2）第二个问题就是在make过程中出现如下问题
   In file included from ./folly/detail/CacheLocality.cpp:17:
   ./folly/../folly/detail/CacheLocality.h:167:5: error: unknown type name 'pthread_t'; did you mean 'thread_t'?
   pthread_t pid = pthread_self();
   ^~~~~~~~~
   thread_t
/Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Platforms/MacOSX.platform/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX10.11.sdk/usr/include/mach/mach_types.h:119:22: note: 'thread_t' declared here
typedef mach_port_t             thread_t;
                               ^
In file included from ./folly/detail/CacheLocality.cpp:17:
./folly/../folly/detail/CacheLocality.h:167:21: error: use of undeclared identifier 'pthread_self'
   pthread_t pid = pthread_self();
                   ^
  解决方法：	 missing #include <ptherad.h> in CacheLocality.h 
          在CacheLocality.h中加入头文件pthread.h   

 
 
 
